    <name>HTML_QuickForm2_Captcha</name>
    <channel>pear.php.net</channel>
    <summary>Captcha package for QuickForm2</summary>
    <description>
        Provides anti-spam measures for forms built with HTML_QuickForm2 by adding a security question that hopefully only humans can answer. Available plugins:
        - ReCaptcha.net
        - Images (Captcha rendered as an image with some obfuscation)
        - Words
        - Figlets (Captcha rendered with an ascii art font)
        - Mathematical equations
        - Mathematical questions (numeral captcha)
    </description>
